      "type": "idea",
      "title": "Keyboard-first navigation",
      "body": "- Deep keyboard shortcuts would let power users navigate nodes, branch out, and resolve items faster without touching the mouse.\n- To make keyboard-first navigation viable, implement a spatial algorithm that selects the target node by finding the closest centroid projection along the selected axis of movement.\n- Need to keep this as an opt-in power user feature to avoid overwhelming casual users with a steep learning curve.",
